Text-SpellChecker version 0.01
==============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Text::Aspell or Text::Hunspell
Storable 
MIME::Base64

